* Monument for the Victims of Manchurian and Mongolian Pioneers{{sfn|小林朗|2004}}
* Meiji University War Dead Memorial Hall

== Visitor Information ==
; Access
* From "Gokoku Shrine Entrance" bus stop on the {{ill|Niigata City Tourist Circulation Bus|ja|新潟市の交通#観光循環バス|12=draft|12=draft}}, a short walk
